==English==

===Noun===
'''V-chip'''

===Etymology===
Stands for ''violence chip'', coined by Tim Collings.

===Meaning===
#''Censorship.'' A form of [[censorship]], or rather [[censorware]], promoted by the William Jefferson Clinton Administration and devised by Tim Collings as a way to allow parents to control the level of objectionable content that their children may see on television.

